window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>I must pay for the sins of my father with the only thing I have of any value....</b></p> <p>My virginity.</p> <p>I will be auctioned. Sold. Shared. Ruined. And then tossed away.</p> <p>It’s a sacrifice I must make to save Daddy, to those seeking revenge for his mounting offenses. But when I become a pawn in a dangerous game played by two rival Russian mafia factions, it seems I might have some leverage.</p> <p>They will fight over me. And in doing so, destroy each other.</p> <p>Daddy might have promised me, but I will turn the tables. It’s suddenly not so cruel anymore. Until I realize I’m no match for the Alekseev brothers. The three of them are ruthless and mean and make me shake with fear. Or is it excitement?</p> <p>This hot, over-the-top Russian Mafia romance is about sexy, dangerous men who'll stop at nothing to pursue and protect the women they want. If you love outrageously naughty stories as a way to indulge your not-so-secret bad girl side, this is for you.</p> <ol> <li><i>Cruel Promise</i></li> <li><i>Brutal Ruin</i></li> <li><i>Vicious Revenge</i></li> </ol>"; 
